- Louie!<br>- Ajussi!

106
00:06:50,610 --> 00:06:52,260
Jsi v pořádku?

107
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:55,780
Bok Sil? Kde je Bok Sil?

108
00:06:55,780 --> 00:06:57,500
