162
00:10:35,690 --> 00:10:38,920
- Nebyl tam.<br>- Kolik jsi jim dala?

163
00:10:38,930 --> 00:10:41,510
- 1 000 000 wonů.<br>- Co?

164
00:10:43,020 --> 00:10:46,390
